{
  "stem": "24111.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the situation went from good to bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I must also tell you that some of the farmers had radios.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And those radios were able to listen to the BBC.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So at that time, we had already knowledge from BBC.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember the victory-- you know, the signals and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we knew how the political situation or the-- or the war was going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was perhaps 18, now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] finally, we got the notification, from the Italian provincial government, that they intend us to be moved to Italy, proper, in internment.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now this is not freedom, like we have in Grad Lesno Brdo, but this is interment-- internment in a little village, by the name of Nonantola, in the vicinity of Modena.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But before we could leave Lesno Brdo, we had also to get permission from the partisans to cross their line.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the partisans, at that time, they wanted the older children, boys and girls, to join them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a matter of fact, one of our girls joined them, by the name of Lili Neuman.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was, later on, killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She and another one were the only person we lost during the whole time for the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] When Joschko made Cernij see our situation, Cernij took the barricades away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What I forgot to tell you is that the partisans, when the fighting with the Italians started, they cut down all the trees on the road going to Horjul, to the main-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] to the main area.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were an isolated building.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they-- actually, the-- the houses were in an-- in an little area called Horjul.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
